# Hooks

## Global hooks (`resources/js/hooks/`)

| Hook | File | Use |
|------|------|-----|
| `useServerPaginationFilters` | `use-server-pagination-filters.ts` | Debounced list search + filter `router.get()` |
| `useHasPermission` | `use-has-permission.ts` | Check `auth.permissions` from Inertia |
| `useSettingsMasterDataCan` | `use-has-permission.ts` | Master-data create/update/delete flags |
| `useViewPreference` | `use-view-preference.ts` | Persist grid/table in localStorage |
| `useDialogState` | `use-dialog-state.tsx` | Toggle one-of-many dialog IDs |
| `useCreatableMasterData` | `use-creatable-master-data.ts` | Inline master-data creation |
| `useAppearance` | `use-appearance.tsx` | Theme light/dark/system |
| `useTwoFactorAuth` | `use-two-factor-auth.ts` | 2FA setup via `useHttp` |
| `useMobile` | `use-mobile.tsx` | Responsive breakpoint |
| `useMutableSelectOptions` | `use-mutable-select-options.ts` | Dynamic select options after create |

**Prefer these before writing new hooks** for the same concern.

## Feature-local hooks

Colocate when logic is domain-specific:

- `features/organization/documents/use-documents-index-filters.ts`
- `features/organization/employees/profile/use-ensure-employee.ts`
- `pages/organization/_hooks/use-employee-profile-form.tsx`

## Naming

- File: `use-kebab-case.ts(x)`
- Export: `usePascalCase` function

## Patterns

**List filters** — wrap `useServerPaginationFilters`:

```tsx
const { searchInput, onSearchChange, onPageChange, onFilterChange } =
    useServerPaginationFilters({ url: branches.url(), search, filters, pagination });
```

Reference: `features/organization/branches/index.tsx`

**Permissions** — never cache permissions outside Inertia shared props:

```tsx
const canCreate = useHasPermission('branches.create');
```

## Avoid

- Global state libraries (Redux, Zustand) — not used in this repo.
- Custom fetch hooks wrapping axios — use Inertia `router` or `useHttp` sparingly.
- Duplicating debounce/pagination logic when `useServerPaginationFilters` fits.
